This paper deals with secure computation, which is a subfield of cryptography (cs.CR). It also focuses on server-aided computation systems, which fall under distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper discusses the optimization of computation time and bandwidth, which are important topics in algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper presents a privacy-preserving application for Android, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL).
